</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_161_r1l25"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Schenk als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒıegl<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_161_r1l26"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_161_r1l27"><expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ wır <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒıegl<ex>er</ex></expan> für vns beſandt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_161_r1l28"><expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒured geſacʒt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> wıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_161_r1l29">er gen <expan>weıſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey vnd lange ʒeıt da wartet da möcht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_161_r1l30">Jm ſeinr ſache kein end noch <expan>auſʒrıchtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> Alſo ſey er </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_162" id="80r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_162_r1l1"><expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> von ſeinr notdurft <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> nachgefarn / Doch ſo ſprıcht er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_162_r1l2">geſcheh Jm noch ein <expan>auſʒrıchtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> von eẅch vmb ſeın ſchulde . ſo well </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_162_r1l3">er ſeıne <expan>erlangte<ex>n</ex></expan> recht vnd brıef <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> abtun vnd <expan>v̈bergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_162_r1l4">wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> </ab>
