</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_161" id="79v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wygeleis Schenken zu Geyrn </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Schenk, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des
                                                  <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Ziegl<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> etc., das
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                                  <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                                  <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                                                  <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Ziegl<ex>er</ex></expan> für uns besandt und
                                                  <expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu red gesaczt
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Der hat uns
                                                  <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, wie er gen
                                                  <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey und lange zeit da
                                                wartet, da möcht im seinr sache kein end noch
                                                  <expan>auszrichtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Also sey er <pb facs="#facs_162" id="80r"/>
<expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> von seinr notdurft
                                                  <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> nachgefarn, doch so
                                                spricht er, gescheh im noch ein
                                                  <expan>auszrichtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> von ewch umb
                                                sein schulde, so well er seine
                                                  <expan>erlangte<ex>n</ex></expan> recht und brief
                                                  <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> abtun und
                                                  <expan>übergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Denn wo wir
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>assu<ex>m</ex>p<ex>ci</ex><hi rend="sup">o<ex>n</ex>is</hi></expan> Marie
                                                  <expan>virg<ex>in</ex>is</expan>.</ab>
</div>
